title: Apon Holo Por
subTitle: Madhabi is cast out by her husband, Abhijit, after a false accusation of rape. Years later, she reunites with him, determined to prove her innocence and uncover the truth behind the tragic misunderstanding.

title: Ladai
subTitle: Raja and Joy are close childhood friends but get separated as they grow up. Raja becomes a police officer and Joy joins the crime world but destiny reunites them and they find themselves at odds.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati has flashbacks to her previous life after touching Lord Shiva's trident. King Himavan announces his decision to arrange the marriage of Parvati and Vindhyak.

title: Chokher Aloye
subTitle: Rajat marries Mrinmoyee after her father pays for his education and makes him the director of his company. However, when Madhuri, his former lover, enters his life, everything changes.

title: Sonar Sansar
subTitle: Abhijit Roy, a retired man, lives with his three children and shelters them from the cruelty of the world. However, as they grow up, they face many challenges in life and must overcome them.

title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Bondhoo
subTitle: A devoted father stands up to obstacles and fights against all odds to win legal custody of his young son.

title: Challenge
subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.

title: Barood
subTitle: Shaon, a loafer, and Jui, an innocent girl are in love with each other. They want to live the life of their dreams together but circumstances turn their lives upside down.

title: Khokababu
subTitle: Abir Roy falls in love with his employer's younger sister. His employer, however, happens to be a dangerous gangster and is overprotective of his sister.

title: Khokababu
subTitle: Abir Roy falls in love with his employer's younger sister. His employer, however, happens to be a dangerous gangster and is overprotective of his sister.

title: Eagoler Chokh
subTitle: A senior police officer and his assistant investigate a young woman's murder. As the case unfolds, he learns more about human psychology and the intricacies of his own mind.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Mainavati and Himavan refuse to accept the proposal for Parvati and Lord Shiva's marriage, and Parvati agrees to fulfil their wish.

title: Yoddha
subTitle: Sole fight of a simpleton against all odds.

title: Nayaner Alo
subTitle: A village singer moves to the city to follow his dreams, where he meets supportive allies who help him navigate fame, ambition and emotional upheaval in an unfamiliar world.

title: Sujan Sakhi
subTitle: A man and a woman fall in love and strive to unite their divided families and overcome the various challenges that threaten their relationship.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Golpo Holeo Shotti
subTitle: Rudra is a pizza delivery man who lives with Anuradha, his girlfriend and an aspiring author. However, a horrific incident changes his life when he starts doubting Anuradha's existence.

title: Satrur Muqubila
subTitle: Awbhoy, a dedicated police officer, develops a deep romantic interest in a young woman attending a job interview while undergoing training.

title: Sangee
subTitle: When Bijay comes to Calcutta for higher studies, he meets Rupa and instantly falls in love with her. However, he is unaware that she is his friend Rana's sister.

title: Sangee
subTitle: When Bijay comes to Calcutta for higher studies, he meets Rupa and instantly falls in love with her. However, he is unaware that she is his friend Rana's sister.

title: Diet
subTitle: A distressed couple strive to make ends meet after losing their land in a dispute. Amina is compelled to opt for prostitution but meets a tragic end due to starvation.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati forsakes her love for Lord Shiva to honour her parents' desire. Later, Mainavati sets terms for approving the marriage arrangement.

title: Lorai
subTitle: The sports minister appoints Sebastian Ryan, an alcoholic and former football player, to form and coach a football team in Purulia. Even though he is sceptical at first, circumstances change his mind.

title: Dabidar
subTitle: A poor couple are heartbroken after their only son deserts them over a petty argument. However, things take a turn after their son relocates to the city and becomes a successful singer.

title: Ranakshetra
subTitle: When Santu protests against availability of drugs and gets murdered by a minister's son, his brother, Raja decides to seek justice on his own after his legal efforts go in vain.

title: Tulkalam
subTitle: Honest, hard-working villagers fight against the forces of industrialisation threatening to take their land away.

title: Champion
subTitle: Jones, a talented and disciplined footballer, is judged by his peers for his financial status. However, when he finds out about his past, he faces a dilemma.

title: Bidroho
subTitle: Uttam's ailing mother dies after not getting proper treatment when the landlord refuses to help them. Later, he decides to exact revenge against the injustice done to him.

title: Badsha: The Don
subTitle: A man who aspires to become a gangster arrives in London to achieve his dreams. However, complications arise when he meets a woman and falls in love with her.
